description: Request for Scoping Opinion for mixed use redevelopment involving the construction of buildings upto 111.550m AOD in height comprising up to 990 dwellings and upto 2,000sq.m of flexible non residential (A1/A2/A3/D1) floor space (demolition of all existing buildings) (Scoping Opinion under Regulation 15 of the Town and Country Planning (Environmental Impact Assessment) Regulations 2017)
